cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) as it deals with sentiment classification in short texts in multiple languages. Other likely sub-categories include "cs.LG" (Machine Learning), "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence), "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval), and "cs.NE" (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as the paper proposes a novel approach using a multi-layer convolutional network and pre-training with weakly-supervised data.
